  "text": "The outlined procedure (steps 1-13) implements a single iteration of the UBS-DM-HS algorithm (or the UBS-DM algorithm if t ¼ 1). More complete elimination of the cosmic ray spikes can be achieved by applying multiple iterations. [CITATION_1] In order to perform multiple iterations, all steps of the algorithm are repeated using the decontaminated hyperspectral data matrix D DC as the new input D in . However, the original hyperspectral data matrix D spike continues to be used in step 13.",
